    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Ak nem\xE1te kameru zapnut\xFA, prirodzene sa menej s\xFAstred\xEDte. Ne\u010Dak\xE1te toti\u017E, \u017Ee v\xE1s niekto oslov\xED"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Ak kameru zapnut\xFA m\xE1te, d\xE1vate lep\u0161\xED pozor. Ale aj vy sa m\xF4\u017Eete za\u010Da\u0165 r\xFDchlo nudi\u0165"), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
